name: Jane Street Group
bossPosition: Global Head of Legal and Compliance
goal:
Jane Street is a global trading firm and liquidity provider with a unique focus on technology and collaborative problem-solving. With offices in London, Amsterdam, New York and Hong Kong we trade across a wide range of over 56,000 financial products, with a focus in ETFs. We commit our own capital and use our global footprint to provide liquidity to markets, as well as directly to some of the largest institutions in the world.

We seek to promote an efficient and healthy capital markets ecosystem through open dialogue with policymakers and engagement with our peers through industry associations.
euInitiatives: Financial services regulations, Investment Firm Regulation (IFR), MIFID II, CRD/CRR
